summary: Do you think Taylor will come out before TS7? I’m never certain what the next step will be and all this theorizing is giving me...
question: Do you think Taylor will come out before TS7? I’m never certain what the next step will be and all this theorizing is giving me a headache. I just need her to express her big gay energy yknow??
answer:
hahahaha! same anon, i love her BDE so much! She totally killed it at the AMA’s, i’m really proud of my queen gay mom.

I don’t think she will come out with a bang, but like some posts that I saw recently, she did a lot of mini coming out lately but our heteronormativity doesn’t see it. 

She just needs to drop the beard eventually (although i kinda like baby gay Joe, he’s so harmless) and she will continue to express her big gay energy, just like she’s been doing this era. 

I expect the next chapter, for her, to be even more her real self: it will be the first album, maybe with a new record company. For example, if she doesn’t use any male pronouns as her love interest: that will be very telling. 

Like so many kaylor friends out there already said: she’ll just need to live her life freely, without having to say anything, and without the need to use a beard: that, for me, will be her coming out.
